    <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> October 26, 2023</p>

    <div class="highlight">
        Kadnex ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application.
    </div>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>

    <h3>Personal Data</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Name, Email Address, and Phone Number</li>
        <li>Physical Address (for service delivery)</li>
        <li>User account credentials (via Firebase Authentication)</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Location Information</h3>
    <p>We may request access to location data to provide services like finding nearby technicians and estimating service arrival times.</p>

    <h3>Usage Data and Device Information</h3>
    <p>Includes device ID, model, OS, and app usage statistics such as time spent and pages viewed.</p>

    <h3>Chat Data</h3>
    <p>Messages exchanged with technicians or support are stored to facilitate service delivery and issue resolution.</p>

    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Create and manage your account</li>
        <li>Process bookings and services</li>
        <li>Enable communication with technicians</li>
        <li>Improve user experience</li>
        <li>Send service-related updates</li>
        <li>Provide customer support</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Sharing Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Technicians:</strong> To fulfill your service requests</li>
        <li><strong>Cloud Providers:</strong> Google Firebase (Authentication, Firestore, Messaging)</li>
        <li><strong>Legal Compliance:</strong> When required by law</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. Security of Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use Firebase’s secure infrastructure along with administrative and technical safeguards. However, no system is completely secure.</p>

    <h2>5. Your Privacy Rights</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Access, update, or delete your data</li>
        <li>Disable location permissions anytime</li>
        <li>Request account deletion from within the app</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>6. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>We may use services like Google Maps. We are not responsible for their privacy practices.</p>

